Thabiso Maretlwaneng bụ onye Botswana na-emepụta ihe nkiri na telivishọn na ihe nkiri. O nwetara onyinye African Achievers Award n'afọ 2015.
Thabiso Maretlwaneng bụ onye mmeri karate, ma nweta agụmakwụkwọ egwuregwu iji mụọ na Swinburne University of Technology na Australia
Dị ka nwa akwụkwọ, o mepụtara ihe ngosi ogologo oge, Head Up, na-eso njem nke ndị na-eto eto ojii gbara ọsọ ndụ na Australia na-anwa ịbanye na ụlọ ọrụ hip hop nke mba ahụ
Akara ụda maka Head Up meriri ihe nrite na 2009 New York International Independent Film and Video Festival.

Ụlọ ọrụ Botswana nke Maretlwaneng bụ Dee-Zone Productions natara ego ndị ntorobịa site na Gọọmentị Botswana. O mepụtara Ntwagolo, ihe nkiri ịrị ise na abụọ na-ele anya na mmetụta nke ọrịa AIDS na Botswana

Pelokgale, usoro nke malitere na 2014, nyochara ime ihe ike dabere na nwoke na nwanyị. Ihe ngosi ntụrụndụ, Pula Power, malitekwara igosi na 2014. N'afọ 2016, e boro Dee-Zone Productions akwụkwọ maka ụgwọ a na-akwụghị ụgwọ.
